  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What is the Phantom Digital Effects IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Phantom Digital Effects IPO<!-- --> is a <b>SME<!-- --> <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> of <!-- -->3063600<!-- --> equity shares</b> of the face value of ₹<!-- -->10<!-- --> aggregating up to ₹<!-- -->29.10<!-- --> Crores. The issue is priced at <span>₹95 per share</span>. The minimum order quantity is <!-- -->1200<!-- -->.</p><p>The <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> <b>opens on <!-- -->October 12, 2022</b>, and <b>closes on <!-- -->October 14, 2022</b>.</p><p>Purva Sharegistry India Pvt Ltd<!-- --> is the registrar for the <!-- -->IPO<!-- -->. The shares are proposed to be listed on <!-- -->NSE SME<!-- -->.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply in Phantom Digital Effects IPO through Zerodha?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Zerodha customers can apply online in <!-- -->Phantom Digital Effects IPO<!-- --> using UPI as a payment gateway. Zerodha customers can apply in <!-- -->Phantom Digital Effects IPO<!-- --> by login into Zerodha Console (back office) and submitting an IPO application form.</p><p><strong>Steps to apply in <!-- -->Phantom Digital Effects IPO<!-- --> through Zerodha</strong></p><ol><li>Visit the Zerodha website and login to Console.</li><li>Go to Portfolio and click the IPOs link.</li><li>Go to the '<!-- -->Phantom Digital Effects IPO<!-- -->' row and click the 'Bid' button.</li><li>Enter your UPI ID, Quantity, and Price.</li><li>Submit IPO application form.</li><li>Visit the UPI App (net banking or BHIM) to approve the mandate.</li></ol><p>Visit <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Application Process Review\">Zerodha IPO Application Process Review</a> for more detail.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When Phantom Digital Effects IPO will open?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The Phantom Digital Effects IPO opens on October 12, 2022 and closes on October 14, 2022.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the lot size of Phantom Digital Effects IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Phantom Digital Effects IPO<!-- --> <b>lot size is <!-- -->1200</b>, and the <b>minimum amount required is <span>₹1,14,000</span></b>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply for Phantom Digital Effects IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>You can apply in <!-- -->Phantom Digital Effects IPO<!-- --> online using either <a href=\"/article/upi-payment-option-ipo-application-explained/382/\">UPI</a> or ASBA as a payment method. ASBA IPO application is available in the net banking of your bank account. UPI IPO application is offered by brokers who don't offer banking services. Read more detail about applying IPO online through <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Review\"><b>Zerodha</b></a>, <a href=\"/broker/upstox/ipo/33/\" title=\"Upstox IPO Review\">Upstox</a>, <a href=\"/broker/5paisa/ipo/4/\" title=\"5Paisa IPO Review\">5Paisa</a>, <a href=\"/broker/edelweiss_broking/ipo/34/\" title=\"Nuvama IPO Review\">Nuvama</a>, <a href=\"/broker/hdfc-securities/ipo/6/\" title=\"HDFC Bank IPO Review\">HDFC Bank</a>, and <a href=\"/broker/sbi-capital/ipo/19/\" title=\"SBI Capital IPO Review\">SBI Bank</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When is Phantom Digital Effects IPO allotment?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The finalization of Basis of Allotment for <!-- -->Phantom Digital Effects IPO<!-- --> will be done on <!-- -->Wednesday, October 19, 2022<!-- -->, and the allotted shares will be credited to your demat account by <!-- -->Friday, October 21, 2022<!-- -->. Check the <a href=\"/ipo_allotment_status/phantom-digital-effects-ipo/1322/\" title=\"Phantom Digital Effects IPO Allotment Status\">Phantom Digital Effects IPO<!-- --> allotment status</a>.</p></div>"
    },
